GENEVA, Switzerland, June 14, 2020/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            For refugees, COVID-19 has become an economic crisis on top of a public health crisis



In a race against time, UNHCR is supporting refugees and IDPs to protect themselves against COVID-19 infections.



The Agency also tries, with limited funding, to buffer the pandemicâ€™s disastrous impact on their family economies.



